This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Distributed Computing (cs.DC) sub-category. Additionally, the paper discusses the structuring technique for fault tolerance, which is related to software engineering (cs.SE). The paper also mentions a prototype architecture, which suggests that it may belong to the Programming Languages (cs.PL) sub-category. The paper also deals with the management of fault tolerance provisions, which is related to system design (cs.SY). Overall, the most likely sub-category is cs.DC, followed by cs.SE, cs.Distributed, cs.PL, and cs.SY.
